rows.label: qev061003_MSG0001
rows.name:
Hmm? Don't see many humans around these parts.
What brings you here? *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0002
rows.name:
Some nasty indigens make their homes here. *fsssh*
It isn't the sort of place one comes without reason.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_JNK0010
rows.name: Request

rows.label: qev061003_SEL0011
rows.name: Show Kiliran the encrypted disk.

rows.label: qev061003_JNK0020
rows.name: Ask

rows.label: qev061003_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask what Kiliran is doing here.

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0003
rows.name: *fsssh* You came looking for me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0004
rows.name: *fsssh* I travel the planet mapping voltant dispersion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0005
rows.name:
That data is crucial to carrying out the mission
Golbogga has given us. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0006
rows.name: *fsssh* And you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0011
rows.name: Ah, they want that disk decrypted. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0012
rows.name:
May I please see it a moment? *fsssh*
It's not a model that is familiar to me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0007
rows.name:
Hmm... I should be able to open it up, though.
*fsssh* It shouldn't take too long.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0008
rows.name:
*fsssh* I hate to make this quid pro quo, but if you
happen to go hunt the xe-dom sarto stalking the area
while you're waiting, I'd appreciate it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0009
rows.name:
That thing has nearly had the better of me a few times
now during my surveying. *fsssh* It's a real pain.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0010
rows.name:
I promise I'll have this disk unlocked and waiting for
you when you get back. Do you mind? *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0013
rows.name:
The encryption is pretty heavy. *fsssh*
Cracking it is going to take a bit more time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0014
rows.name:
*fsssh* I'd appreciate it if you would go hunt the
xe-dom sarto for me in the meantime.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0015
rows.name:
That thing has interrupted my voltant dispersion
mapping time and again, and all the delays are
starting to add up. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0023
rows.name:
You got him? Blessed day! *fsssh* Now I can finally
make some real progress with my survey work.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0024
rows.name:
*fsssh* And as luck would have it, I just finished up
here. Your disk is decrypted and ready to go.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0025
rows.name:
It looked like it holds data on Bedun before the
Day of Regrowth. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0026
rows.name:
It may just offer a glimpse at the face of Golbogga
the creator himself. *fsssh* I'll admit that I'm curious.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_JNK0050
rows.name: Query

rows.label: qev061003_SEL0051
rows.name: Ask Kiliran if he wants to view the contents of the disk.

rows.label: qev061003_JNK0060
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: qev061003_SEL0061
rows.name: Tell Kiliran that you're curious too.

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0027
rows.name:
*fsssh* I know Golbogga made us, and I know that it's
his will we devoltanize.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0028
rows.name:
Past that, my only concern is surveying the land and
making it easier to carry out the mission. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0029
rows.name:
You humans' intellectual curiosity is a wonderful thing.
You're interested even in the history of others. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0030
rows.name:
But I'm afraid that's one truth I don't have the courage
to learn. *fsssh* I ask that you wait and reveal it to a
Zaruboggan who does.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0031
rows.name:
*fsssh* Now if you'll excuse me.
I still have a lot of land left to survey.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev061003_MSG0032
rows.name: I pray you walk always in Golbogga's grace. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]
